Mortimer: Hello. I would need a potion of sorts to [color={bold_color}]temporarily incapacitate[/color] some bad people, and I would need it in [color={bold_color}]2 days[/color]. Can I count on you to help me out?

Mortimer: Thank you. I'll be back in 2 days to pick it up.

set {request} = "Potion to temporarily incapacitate some bad people"
set {deadline} = 2.0
[signal arg="order"]